{"tid":220083,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插沙］電腦瘋狂hang機，換完ram都冇用，仲好似有燶味","createTime":"2017-04-27T16:54:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T13:39:58.000Z","uid":106064,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f07ca6f36fabc9a7f0daa84351312b98b895f486","tid":220083,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T16:54:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n部電腦都用左四年，但近排成日我打機/睇片時hang機，之後要重開<br />\n拎去比人整，話係ram有問題（2x4GB)<br />\n拎去保養換完之後係冇hang得咁密，但情況越趨嚴重<br />\n今日仲短時間內hang兩次（之前一日/幾日一次）<br />\n仲唔知係咪有陣燶味<br />\n<br />\nCheck過主機板冇爆電容，抆哂d ram主機板正常地有響<br />\n兩個ram槽分別試過開機冇問題<br />\n<br />\n所以想請教各位巴打<br />\n1.仲會唔會係主機板出事？<br />\n2.ram槽出事？<br />\n3.火牛？<br />\n4.hard disk硬碟?(近排開機時主機有吱吱聲，唔知係咪壞？<br />\n5. CPU?(check過事發前50-60度）<br />\n6.顯卡？（nividia gtx 650ti)有時打機會話驅動程式停止回應，但通常唔會hang,我諗唔關事？）<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打們可以幫下手，小弟好窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，再拎去整怕比人水，想試下自己搞唔搞到，感激不盡，連登有愛"},{"pid":"ab71bc6b09ace1136e84f005b0045c8730cfb277","tid":220083,"uid":46321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:06:44.000Z","msg":"用呢個睇睇電壓正唔正常，順便睇埋溫度<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cpuid.com/softwares/hwmonitor-pro.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpuid.com%2Fsoftwares%2Fhwmonitor-pro.html&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=74bed300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cpuid.com/softwares/hwmonitor-pro.html</a><br />\n<br />\nHard disk係少少吱吱聲定係格格聲先？格格聲就快Backup啦，死得<br />\n<br />\n如果上面嘅嘢都正常，咁試試換埋Hard disk嘅電源線同SATA線"},{"pid":"fc9a7815e8f9355c468850581d2ac7f71de41799","tid":220083,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:17:26.000Z","msg":"顯你老母卡"},{"pid":"f2a94f4678762eec847e666ba21517a22102cd1c","tid":220083,"uid":54778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T17:23:49.000Z","msg":"試過有燶味 之後發現係火牛 一抆發現插電個位直頭融咗一忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果驅動程式就通常係display card 出事"},{"pid":"3fefbdcc31ea42b8ea1d028373c8a4143d301f2e","tid":220083,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:42:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用呢個睇睇電壓正唔正常，順便睇埋溫度<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cpuid.com/softwares/hwmonitor-pro.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cpuid.com%2Fsoftwares%2Fhwmonitor-pro.html&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513Z4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=74bed300\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cpuid.com/softwares/hwmonitor-pro.html</a><br />\n<br />\nHard disk係少少吱吱聲定係格格聲先？格格聲就快Backup啦，死得<br />\n<br />\n如果上面嘅嘢都正常，咁試試換埋Hard disk嘅電源線同SATA線</blockquote><br />\n點為之正常？<br />\nHard disk少少吱吱聲"},{"pid":"8e10a53b6e0b895f3ed3495ddc34acacba492a7e","tid":220083,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:46:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過有燶味 之後發現係火牛 一抆發現插電個位直頭融咗一忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果驅動程式就通常係display card 出事</blockquote><br />\n但驅動程式停止回應多數只會黑幾秒mon就冇事<br />\n同埋佢成日停止回應唔係nividia軟件問題咩？係我張顯壞左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ca47bf3cb741e3166dac3bd9c205486de91607","tid":220083,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T02:13:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bf619d0e266762c3966990dfa3f5c7e0c55ac820","tid":220083,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T02:13:29.000Z","msg":"Pushh"},{"pid":"1df2c5785c43ba48ee6cf1edeeb9c56b550d7c9c","tid":220083,"uid":3108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T02:19:25.000Z","msg":"顯你老團母卡"},{"pid":"129df61b15a4e39aa6c7e0d46b47b011ef57d645","tid":220083,"uid":106064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/8cf92d7aa0856e8001969a